    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If I'm using the {{REQUEST_METHOD}} or {{$this-&gt;_request-&gt;getMethod()}} in my controller, I get "undefined index" while executing tests.</p>

<p>I guess the expected behaviour would be {{GET}}. An intermediate fix is to use {{setMethod('GET')}} in your test case.</p>

